<div id="dinopanel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="dinotab-ecosystem" style="padding:16px">
<div>
<div style="margin-bottom:12px">
<div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800">🌍 Ancient ecosystems</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">Not all dinosaurs lived together. Each rock formation is a snapshot of one place and time. Pick a site to meet its whole community.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-bottom:10px;max-height:132px;overflow-y:auto">
<button aria-pressed="true" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid #15803d;background:#15803d;color:#fff">Morrison (23)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Dinosaur Park (16)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Yixian (15)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Hell Creek (12)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Djadochta (12)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Nemegt (12)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Shishugou (9)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Horseshoe Canyon (7)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Wessex (6)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Cedar Mountain (5)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Huincul (5)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Judith River (5)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Tendaguru (5)</button>
<button aria-pressed="false" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">Portezuelo (5)</button>
