<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">A lightweight reconstruction lab. The model is procedural and scale-aware: it visualizes evidence and uncertainty instead of pretending we know every detail.</div>
