</div>
<div role="group" aria-label="Cretaceous lasted about 79 million years, from 145 to 66 million years ago, with 250 listed dinosaurs." style="margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:3px;background:#22c55e;display:inline-block">
</span>
<span style="font-weight:800;font-size:15px">Cretaceous</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">145 to 66 million years ago</span>
</div>
<div role="progressbar" aria-label="Cretaceous duration on the Mesozoic timeline" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="229" aria-valuenow="79" aria-valuetext="Cretaceous lasted about 79 million years, from 145 to 66 million years ago, with 250 listed dinosaurs." style="height:10px;border-radius:6px;background:#22c55e33;margin:6px 0;overflow:hidden">
<div style="height:100%;width:34%;background:#22c55e">
</div>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-bottom:4px">Peak dinosaur diversity, ended by an asteroid impact.</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px">
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌡️ Warm, with high seas and no polar ice caps for much of it.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌿 Flowering plants spread quickly and reshaped ecosystems.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌊 Shallow seas flooded the continents, including North America.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px">
<button aria-label="Open T. rex" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">T. rex</button>
